<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Security Alert</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #e74c3c; color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
        .content { background: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
        .alert-box { background: #ffebee; border-left: 4px solid #e74c3c; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0; }
        .details { background: #fff; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .button { display: inline-block; background: #e74c3c; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; color: #666; font-size: 12px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>üö® Security Alert</h1>
        <p>Account activity detected</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{firstName}} {{lastName}},</h2>
        
        <div class="alert-box">
            <strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Important:</strong> We detected the following activity on your {{appName}} account:
        </div>
        
        <div class="details">
            <h3>Activity Details:</h3>
            <p><strong>Action:</strong> {{action}}</p>
            <p><strong>Location:</strong> {{location}}</p>
            <p><strong>Device:</strong> {{device}}</p>
            <p><strong>Time:</strong> {{timestamp}}</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>If this was you, no action is needed. However, if you don't recognize this activity:</p>
        
        <ol>
            <li><strong>Change your password immediately</strong></li>
            <li><strong>Review your account activity</strong></li>
            <li><strong>Check your authorized devices</strong></li>
            <li><strong>Enable two-factor authentication if not already active</strong></li>
        </ol>
        
        <a href="{{appUrl}}/account/security" class="button">Secure My Account</a>
        
        <p>For additional support, contact our security team immediately if you believe your account has been compromised.</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>The {{appName}} Security Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>{{appName}} | <a href="{{appUrl}}">{{appUrl}}</a></p>
        <p>This is an automated security alert. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>